# Local development secrets. Copy to .dev.vars and fill in.
# .dev.vars is gitignored. Never commit real secret values.

# Bearer token for the API during local dev (there is no Cloudflare Access in
# front of `wrangler dev`). Call the API with: Authorization: Bearer <this value>.
# Use a long random string. See SECURITY.md for the production tradeoff.
AUTH_TOKEN=replace-with-a-long-random-string

# Only if you use Web Push locally. Generate with: npx web-push generate-vapid-keys
# VAPID_PRIVATE=

# Only if you exercise the in-app domain onboarding flow locally. Scope narrowly.
# CF_API_TOKEN=

# Optional. HMAC key for the /api/media image-token signer (inline cid + remote
# image proxy). Falls back to AUTH_TOKEN when unset, so it is optional in dev.
# IMG_PROXY_SECRET=
